  "description": "A nighttime panoramic view showcases a vibrant fireworks display over a city skyline and a long bridge. The fireworks explode in a variety of colors \u2013 white, green, and red \u2013 illuminating the dark sky. Below, the city is a tapestry of illuminated buildings, creating a warm glow. A prominent bridge with lit-up structures spans a body of water, with red and white lights marking its length. The water appears calm and reflects some of the city lights. The composition creates a sense of celebration and urban beauty.",
